#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:1
msgid "事件流系统（Event Stream）"
msgstr "Event Stream"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:3
msgid ""
"事件流是 SimpleLLMFunc v0.5.0+ 引入的高级特性，允许你实时观察 ReAct 循环的完整执行过程。通过启用事件流，你可以监控 LLM"
" 调用、工具调用、流式响应等所有关键环节，实现更精细的控制和更好的用户体验。"
msgstr ""
"Event stream is an advanced feature introduced in SimpleLLMFunc v0.5.0+ that"
" allows you to observe the complete execution process of the ReAct loop in "
"real-time. By enabling event streams, you can monitor all key steps such as "
"LLM calls, tool calls, and streaming responses, enabling finer control and a"
" better user experience."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:5
msgid "在当前版本中，事件流还提供了统一来源元数据（`EventYield.origin`），用于稳定识别主会话与 fork 子会话。"
msgstr ""
"In the current version, Event Stream also provides unified source metadata "
"(`EventYield.origin`) for stable identification of main sessions and fork "
"child sessions."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:7
msgid "**适用范围**：事件流系统同时支持 `@llm_chat` 和 `@llm_function` 装饰器，提供统一的事件观测体验。"
msgstr ""
"**Scope of application**: The event streaming system supports both "
"`@llm_chat` and `@llm_function` decorators, providing a unified event "
"observation experience."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:9
msgid "概述"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:11
msgid "什么是事件流？"
msgstr "What is an event stream?"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:13
msgid "事件流（Event Stream）是一种观察者模式的应用，它会在 ReAct 循环执行过程中产生一系列事件，包括："
msgstr ""
"Event Stream is an application of the Observer pattern, which generates a "
"series of events during the execution of the ReAct loop, including:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:15
msgid "**LLM 调用事件**：LLM 调用开始、流式 chunk 到达、调用结束"
msgstr "**LLM Call Event**: LLM call start, streamed chunk arrival, call end"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:16
msgid "**工具调用事件**：工具调用开始、执行完成、批次处理"
msgstr ""
"**Tool Call Event**: Tool call starts, execution completes, batch processing"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:17
msgid "**ReAct 循环事件**：循环开始、迭代开始/结束、循环结束"
msgstr "**ReAct Loop Events**: Loop Start, Iteration Start/End, Loop End"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:18
msgid "**执行统计**：Token 使用量、执行耗时、调用次数等"
msgstr ""
"**Execution Statistics**: Token usage, execution time, call count, etc."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:20
msgid "为什么需要事件流？"
msgstr "Why is event streaming needed?"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:22
msgid "在传统使用中，你只能获得最终的响应结果。而事件流提供了："
msgstr ""
"In traditional usage, you only get the final response. Event streams offer:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:24
msgid "**实时监控**：观察 LLM 和工具调用的实时状态"
msgstr ""
"**Real-time monitoring**: Observe the real-time status of LLM and tool calls"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:25
msgid "**性能分析**：获取详细的执行统计和性能指标（Token 用量、耗时等）"
msgstr ""
"**Performance Analysis**: Obtain detailed execution statistics and "
"performance metrics (token usage, time consumption, etc.)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:26
msgid "**自定义 UI**：基于事件构建丰富的用户界面（进度条、流式显示等）"
msgstr ""
"**Custom UI**: Build rich user interfaces based on events (progress bars, "
"streaming displays, etc.)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:27
msgid "**调试支持**：深入了解 ReAct 循环的执行细节"
msgstr ""
"**Debug Support**: Deep dive into the execution details of the ReAct loop"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:28
msgid "**状态管理**：通过 Wrapper 模式实现 Context Compression、状态持久化等"
msgstr ""
"**State Management**: Context Compression, state persistence, etc. are "
"implemented through the Wrapper pattern."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:30
msgid "设计哲学：Agent 作为无状态函数"
msgstr "Design Philosophy: Agent as a Stateless Function"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:32
msgid "SimpleLLMFunc 遵循一个核心设计哲学：**Agent 本身是一个函数，不管理自己的状态**。"
msgstr ""
"SimpleLLMFunc follows a core design philosophy: **The Agent itself is a "
"function and does not manage its own state**."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:34
msgid "这意味着："
msgstr "This means:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:36
msgid "✅ **无状态设计**：`@llm_chat` 装饰的函数是纯函数，每次调用都是独立的"
msgstr ""
"✅ **Stateless Design**: Functions decorated with `@llm_chat` are pure "
"functions, and each call is independent."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:37
msgid "✅ **状态外置**：所有状态（包括 `history`）都通过参数传入和返回值传出"
msgstr ""
"✅ **State Externalization**: All states (including `history`) are passed in "
"through parameters and passed out through return values"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:38
msgid "✅ **可组合性**：通过 wrapper 函数实现状态管理和高级功能"
msgstr ""
"✅ **Composability**: State management and advanced features are implemented "
"through wrapper functions"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:40
msgid "**为什么这样设计？**"
msgstr "Why is it designed this way?"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:42
msgid "**函数式编程**：符合函数式编程理念，易于测试和推理"
msgstr ""
"**Functional Programming**: Conforms to the functional programming paradigm,"
" easy to test and reason about"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:43
msgid "**灵活性**：状态管理完全由用户控制，可以实现各种自定义逻辑"
msgstr ""
"**Flexibility**: State management is fully controlled by the user, allowing "
"for various custom logic implementations"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:44
msgid "**可扩展性**：通过 wrapper 函数可以轻松添加 Context Compression、状态持久化等功能"
msgstr ""
"**Scalability**: Functions like Context Compression and state persistence "
"can be easily added through wrapper functions."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:46
msgid "**如何实现状态管理和修改？**"
msgstr "How to achieve state management and modification?"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:48
msgid "通过事件流，你可以："
msgstr "Through the event stream, you can:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:50
msgid "**监控状态**：通过事件获取 Agent 的内部状态信息（消息历史、工具调用等）"
msgstr ""
"**Monitoring Status**: Obtain the internal state information (message "
"history, tool calls, etc.) of the Agent through events."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:51
msgid "**修改状态**：在 wrapper 函数中拦截和修改 `history`，实现 Context Compression 等功能"
msgstr ""
"**Modify status**: Intercept and modify `history` in the wrapper function to"
" implement features such as Context Compression."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:52
msgid "**状态持久化**：在 wrapper 中实现状态的保存和恢复"
msgstr ""
"**State persistence**: Implement state saving and restoration within the "
"wrapper"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/event_stream.md:54
msgid "下面我们将详细展示如何通过 wrapper 函数实现这些功能。"
msgstr ""
"Next, we will show in detail how to implement these functions through "
"wrapper functions."

